mpiti director and coo also is ceo of glass house graphics isen robbins cipo and aimee schoof cbdo are both from intrinsic value films and red giant media chris crosby is cto and the ceo of keenspot entertainment internet personality mark markiplier fischbach joined the board in november  contents  works  comics  webcomics and digital comics  giantsize comics  collections and novels  collections  graphic novels  film  television  video games and apps  history  partners  controversy  references  external links worksedit comicsedit webcomics and digital comicsedit red giant publishes a variety of webcomics with strategic partner keenspot including wayward sons legends exposure jade warriors buzzboy medusas daughter katrina and porcelain these comics are then collected as digital collections on comixologynonprimary source needed giantsize comicsedit red giants giantsize comics is a print comic book line of free adsupported anthology titles set to debut on may   as part of free comic book day before their full weekly launch in july  the four free giantsize titles include giantsize action wayward sons  tesla giantsize adventure magika  the first daughter giantsize fantasy duel identity  pandoras blog and giantsize thrills shadow children  darchon in august  it was announcednonprimary source needed that mort castle will be scripting the red giant entertainment comic book darchon an ongoing feature of their giantsize comics line of free print comic book titles set to debut on may   as part of free comic book day darchon is scheduled to appear monthly in giantsize thrills the companies horror title in november  it was announced that dc comics veteran brian augustyn had been hired as story editor for the giantsize comics line on august   red giant announced that larry hama is writing the companys new monster isle monthly series debuting this novembernonprimary source needed on august   red giant announced that brian augustyn is scripting a new amped comic series debuting in 